        <Parent_String>diatonic harps [300209199], frame harps [300194023], harps (chordophones) [300042047], chordophones [300041641], sound devices by acoustical characteristics [300041621], sound devices (equipment) [300387677], Sound Devices (hierarchy name) [300041619], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
